29034a39724a4e5ab8eb889f757f","tid":130213,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:39:40.000Z","msg":"走完爛Grade<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">利申：懶</span>"},{"pid":"4ce25de7de40d4cca83c4bd4e473f9d6b6f89513","tid":130213,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:41:33.000Z","msg":"好撚有用<br />\n<br />\n港大JT Yu嘅algebra course<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNM Ngai嘅complex analysis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好過吞書好多"},{"pid":"50e46bb382300e50b8deae9f6dc14048b2df8ffd","tid":130213,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:46:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇你咩科，Nursing JJ表示上少堂都唔掂<br />\n雖然notes都有曬基本嘢<br />\n但係最新既藥種真係要上堂聽<br />\n仲有藥物副作用種種都唔一樣<br />\nnotes寫就一味噁心嘔吐<br />\n但係幾種藥噁心嘔吐既程度都唔同<br />\n <br />\nnotes寫五六種藥，但係professor 又話有兩種HA已經唔用<br />\n<br />\n有時又因為版權問題<br />\nnote上面 唔可以有太多人哋書嘅圖<br />\n或者notes 印咗出嚟之後矇查查<br />\n有時要靠 professor 手畫畀我哋睇<br />\n<br />\nprofessor喺堂上面有會做少少分享<br />\n只係唔同藥物嘅花名<br />\n已經可以講半足個鐘<br />\n<br />\n仲未計教實習既lecture<br />\n齋睇notes學插喉學打針真係等死</blockquote><br />\n我都係讀nursing 但好似覺得有lecture完全聽唔入耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上全部notes都係返去自己睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e57361d13e87d3f7ae4d483e68c412565669560","tid":130213,"uid":2716,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T02:57:25.000Z","msg":"成日走堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> gpa&gt;3.5"},{"pid":"a76d67dbe641857f0af80b395b3de6f56fb79590","tid":130213,"uid":13768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:18:12.000Z","msg":"堂堂上同走曬全部堂既course個grade都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"375a78dea9bf9dd1b01e969b6d10967e2767b54e","tid":130213,"uid":59136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:19:34.000Z","msg":"好辛苦起到身上lecture<br />\n但完全聽唔撚明<br />\n（其實個lecture唔差 但呢真係太難）<br />\n<br />\n重點：有上堂唔代表會識"},{"pid":"ba37b6b5acd0d6901b7ef40be5125c15b2dbe446","tid":130213,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:20:21.000Z","msg":"好多人搞唔清楚走堂同成績嘅關係<br />\n<br />\n好多時係你識嗰個course嘅嘢，追得上先敢走堂<br />\n而唔係因為走堂所以成績好咁戇鳩"},{"pid":"aa183d49666eddd00b74f6de9fafdf363cacadfb","tid":130213,"uid":81234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>堂堂上同走曬全部堂既course個grade都一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依個真"},{"pid":"b6f11982d2469fc66085aefaf0d844bd0bec019c","tid":130213,"uid":7687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:22:50.000Z","msg":"上左幾次都知個lecturer教唔教到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教唔到不如唔上好過<br />\n我而家大部份堂係為左陪fd先上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de5c2b344d8ce94b7e62368837f5cd89f8e6e82a","tid":130213,"uid":56425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T03:38:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>lecturer已經係大陸人講英文唔清唔楚<br />\n上lecture為左趕進度又教鬼死咁快<br />\nskip好多野<br />\n上左同唔上都無咩分別<br />\n<br />\n不過試過有個lecture mid term第一題係佢叫咩名同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame here<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有題MC 問Lecturer 全名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":