f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\npresentation就算唔係自己組都一定要出席<br />\n會要我地寫返feedback比每組 張feedback計入project分<br />\n好啦 就算我好學霸咁上曬啲堂<br />\n好多lecturer都廢嘅 試過見到我有本reference book<br />\n佢問我借嚟備課 又問我本書嘅重點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如我教啦？<br />\n啲notes又hea喎 一個concept兩三句講完<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上我個系係無dayoff嘅 忙到甩肺<br />\n正常人都唔會借reference book自習<br />\n結果做project組組啲concept都錯撚曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0892204a3c17299ac13885aaf5477639bb8c8a0","tid":130213,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:35:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有個prof midterm問who is teaching you the course<br />\n<br />\nFinal叫人用講過既concept，引用例子分析佢係點既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nmgmt2110<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個咁無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔係知既咩？之前你好似有提過</blockquote><br />\n我無聽過呢件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢事爆係邊個題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個教得好好，好grade既local 女prof<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/03.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e814d23b912b4818788babc233d91741ce3e3f2","tid":130213,"uid":14185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T17:25:23.000Z","msg":"其實好睇人既姐<br />\n一來睇你個lecturer係咪個d學術成就好高，經驗好豐富，但教書救到垃撚圾既人<br />\n二來睇你自己偏好既讀書方法<br />\n<br />\n我就係偏向視覺型既讀書方法<br />\n聽lecture既話淨係專心到十五分鐘<br />\n但睇書就可以專心睇足幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma